dapt.Config.create('config.json')
conf = dapt.Config('config.json')
conf.config['abc'] = {'a': 1, 'b': 2, 'c': {'aa': 11, 'bb': 22}}
conf.update_config()
os.remove('config.json')
assert conf.get_value(['abc', 'c', 'aa']
    ) == 11, 'Config.get_value(["abc", "c", "aa"],recursive=False): Config did not find the correct value.'
